[thinking] I need to think about possibly moving nested classes that seem duplicative. For example, I might consider the instantiation of JAXB context factory implementations. Are they tied to OSGi-bound classes? There's a duplicate in ServiceLoaderUtilTest that could create confusion. I wonder if ContextFinderTest could handle loading the JAXB context factory implementations that are returned by the OSGi locator for these bound classes, even when the service resource is hidden.
